      "description": "Reliable project candidate with a strong-running drivetrain, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. It shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in places, but it starts, runs, and drives, making it a great budget entry for someone who wants usable transportation or a platform to sort and improve. A good fit for a hands-on buyer looking for solid mechanical bones at an approachable price.",
